metadata.description: First track from the SPEEDHOUSE project where the initial idea of the album truly coalesced. I was thinking how to take what I loved about house music but mashed up with the feeling of 140bpm dance music. This among the other records on the project represented to me a perfect amalgamation of influences ranging from techno, speed garage, and hard dance - but infusing it with a more fun melodic vibe and less serious nature. New Art specifically made for the sound.xyz release. Much love - luca
